; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/diff-so-fancy.md

% diff-so-fancy, common

# Colorize `diff`
diff <__u___unified_> <path_to_file1> <path_to_file2> | diff-so-fancy

# Set `diff-so-fancy` to colorize the output during Git's interactive staging
git config --global interactive.diffFilter "diff-so-fancy --patch"
